SKIP LINKS
=================================
Needs to be added as direct child of the #wrapper element,  Need to update href to div id of main content element

HTML
----
<a class="skip-link hidden" href="#section-content">Skip to content</a>



BUILT IN ACCORDION HTML STRUCTURE
=================================

REPLACEMENTS
------------
{#}      : unique number/identifier for each accordion on page
{TITLE}  : title of the accordion
{CONTENT}: content of the accordion

HTML
----
<div id="sfw-accordion-{#}" class="sfw-accordion">
    <input id="sfw-accordion-action-{#}" type="checkbox" />
    <label for="sfw-accordion-action-{#}" role="tab">{TITLE}</label>
    <div class="sfw-accordion-content-wrap" role="tabpanel"><div class="sfw-accordion-content">{CONTENT}</div></div>
</div>
